sentences.english: This paper deals with the floristic statistics, analysis of the 418 species on wild ligneous plants.

sentences.english: Any of several other woody plants, as in the genera Carpinus and Nothofagus.

sentences.english: Endogenous auxin, or indole-3-acetic acid (IAA), plays a central role during root induction in woody plants.

sentences.english: The growth state and distribution features of these evergreen plants are analyzed.

sentences.english: A tree is a tall, woody plant that usually has one main stem, or trunk.

sentences.english: Herb pollen percentage was slightly higher than that of arboreal pollen during the flood period.

sentences.english: Up to a quarter of all the woody growth in some rainforests may be lianas .

sentences.english: Fertilizer is still necessary, and woody plants need the occasional pruning.
sentences.chinese: 施肥就仍然有必要，而木本植物就偶尔要做修枝。

sentences.english: All these ligneous plants are imported from Russia.
sentences.chinese: 这些木本植物都是从俄国进口而来。
